      "writtenOn": "2018-07-11T20:28:00Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Yeah. In fact, FetchAndDeployInstance should also be internal, EnsurePackages should be the only public API to install/remove stuff.\n\nUnfortunately, FetchAndDeployInstance is currently used by \"friendly\" CLI (\"cipd install ...\"), so hiding it is not possible currently. \"cipd install\" should learn to just modify ensure file and call EnsurePackages.",
